    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Slice the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>baby button mushrooms</strong> in half</p><p>Cut the <strong>tomatoes</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 3,
