    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric </strong>and <strong>ground cumin </strong>to the pan</p><p>Increase the heat to medium and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and <strong>mango chutney</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your <strong>mango stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1581675285447-x200.jpg",
