    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once cooked, fluff the<strong> </strong>rice with a fork and stir through the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>– this is your <strong>coriander rice</strong></p>",
