    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mushroom rogan josh </strong>with the <strong>coriander rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and <strong>roasted portobello mushroom slices</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
